creator: F. Zander
descriptionHtml:
Create your own cookbook with our food recipes app. Alone or with friends you can collect your own recipes easily. Also you can create a copy of the database and save it in the /RecipesApp folder. So you do not lose any data in your own recipe book.

From time to time it is also recommended to make a backup of the hole folder /RecipesApp on another location

- Choose your own currency sign
- There are no recipes at the moment.
- In the settings you can adjust the color theme to your taste.
- When saving a new recipe, you can enter the recipe name, category, difficulty, cost in euros, preparation time, ingredients and instructions for the preparation of the ingredients.
- Create your own categories for the recipes
- The database for the recipes can be saved as a backup
- A photo can be saved for each recipe
- All data is stored in the / RecipesApp folder on your smartphone.
The recipe book is constantly expanded for e.g. Error corrections or crashes (if any)

Our recipes app free is perfect for pasta recipes, vegetarian recipes, cake recipes, cookie recipes, noodle recipes, salad recipes, barbecue recipes, back recipes or even cake recipes and many more and everything is properly stored in different categories.
